2. cs.DB (Databases) - The paper discusses the natural join and inner union operations in databases and proposes lattice theory as an alternative to relational algebra. 
3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper deals with the embeddability problem in lattices, which is a topic related to data structures. 
4. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper discusses the undecidability of the quasiequational theory of relational lattices, which is a topic related to computational complexity. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes lattice theory as an algebraic approach to the theory of databases, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence.
